    /// [`KwargPathKind::LABELS`] (`[&'static str; 3]`),
    /// [`MacroDefHead::KEYWORDS`] (`[&'static str; 3]`),
    /// [`crate::ast::Atom::BOOL_LITERALS`] (`[&'static str; 2]`), and
    /// [`crate::ast::QuoteForm::PREFIXES`] (`[&'static str; 4]`) — every
